0to%20meet%20him%2C%20but%20I%20was%20not%20allowed...%20We%20said%20earlier%20also%20and%20even%20today%20we%20will%20say%20the%20same%20about%20the%20allegation%20of%20giving%20slow%20poison.%20On%20March%2019%2C%20he%20was%20poisoned%20in%20the%20dinner.%20We%20will%20move%20to%20the%20judiciary%2C%20we%20have%20full%20faith%20in%20it...%26quot%3B%20Umar%20Ansari%2C%20son%20of%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPost-mortem%20will%20be%20conducted%20tomorrow%2C%20after%20that%2C%20they%20will%20give%20us%20the%20body.%20We%20will%20then%20follow%20with%20the%20further%20process%20(cremation)...%20My%20father%20alleged%20being%20given%20a%20slow%20poison...%20Around%20five%20doctors%20panel%20has%20been%20made%20(for%20carrying%20out%20the%20post-mortem)%2C%26quot%3B%20Umar%20Ansari%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20body%20of%20gangster-turned-politician%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%20has%20been%20sent%20for%20post-mortem%20at%20Banda%20Medical%20College%20Hospital%2C%20Banda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20death%20of%20the%20five%20time%20MLA%2C%20several%20political%20leaders%20extended%20their%20condolences.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20AIMIM%20president%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20expressed%20his%20grief%20in%20support%20of%20the%20family%20of%20Mukhtar%20Ansari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20pray%20to%20Allah%20to%20forgive%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%20and%20give%20patience%20to%20his%20family%20and%20his%20loved%20ones.%20The%20people%20of%20Ghazipur%20lost%20their%20favourite%20son%20and%20brother.%20Mukhtar%20Saheb%20had%20made%20serious%20allegations%20against%20the%20administration%20that%20he%20had%20been%20poisoned.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20government%20did%20not%20pay%20any%20attention%20to%20his%20treatment.%20Condemnable%20and%20regrettable%2C%26quot%3B%20AIMIM%20president%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20leader%20Ameeque%20Jamei%20demanded%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20of%20Mukhta