0of%20lava%20and%20flame.%20she%20looks%20threatening%20and%20powerful%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660338c916bde8d4ead273c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221532%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20planet%20engulfed%20in%20flame%20in%20%26quot%3B3%20Body%20Problem.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20English%20translation%20of%20Liu's%20novels%2C%20the%20alien%20colonizers%20are%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Btrisolarans%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20reference%20to%20their%20tri-solar%20world.%20The%20organization%20preparing%20for%20their%20arrival%20on%20Earth%20is%20the%20ETO%3A%20the%20Earth-Trisolaris%20Organization.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20Netflix%20series%2C%20they're%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BSan-Ti.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20moniker%20in%20the%20show%20is%20a%20reference%20to%20Ye%20Wenjie's%20first%20contact%20with%20the%20aliens%20while%20she%20was%20based%20in%20China.%20%26quot%3BS%C4%81n%20t%C7%90-r%C3%A9n%26quot%3B%20means%20%26quot%3Bthree-body%20people%26quot%3B%20in%20Chinese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20show%20doesn't%20explore%20the%20factions%20of%20the%20ETO%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mike%20evans%20in%203%20body%20problem%2C%20sitting%20at%20a%20desk%20with%20an%20old%20school%20microphone%20and%20transmitter%20box%20on%20it.%20there's%20a%20shelf%20behind%20him%20with%20a%20photo%20of%20someone%2C%20and%20a%20small%20box%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6603388716bde8d4ead273aa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJonathan%20Pryce%20as%20Mike%20Evans%20in%20%26quot%3B3%20Body%20Problem.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EEd%20Miller%2FNetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20books%2C%20the%20ETO%20has%20a%20few%20different%20factions%3A%20the%20Adventists%2C%20who%20want%20the%20Trisolarans%20to%20des