f%20climate%20change%20on%20Earth's%20rotation%2C%20potentially%20delaying%20the%20need%20for%20a%20'negative%20leap%20second'%20by%20three%20years.%20The%20delicate%20balance%20between%20Earth's%20rotation%20and%20atomic%20time%20poses%20challenges%20for%20global%20timekeeping%20infrastructure%2C%20with%20uncertainties%20and%20skepticism%20surrounding%20the%20introduction%20of%20a%20negative%20leap%20second.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Fenvironment%2Fclimate-change-is-even-messing-with-how-we-measure-time-says-study%2Farticleshow%2F108859889.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Fenvironment%2Fclimate-change-is-even-messing-with-how-we-measure-time-says-study%2Famp_articleshow%2F108859889.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Fenvironment%2Fclimate-change-is-even-messing-with-how-we-measure-time-says-study%2Famp_articleshow%2F108859889.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gangster-Politician%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%20Dies%20Of%20Cardiac%20Arrest%20At%2063%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJailed%20gangster-turned-politician%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%20has%20died%20of%20a%20cardiac%20arrest%20after%20being%20hospitalised%20on%20Thursday%20evening.%20The%20five-time%20former%20MLA%20from%20Mau%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20had%20been%20in%20jail%20in%20the%20state%20and%20in%20Punjab%20since%202005.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20medical%20bulletin%20said%20the%2063-year-old%2C%20who%20was%20lodged%20in%20a%20jail%20in%20UP's%20Banda%2C%20had%20been%20taken%20to%20the%20Rani%20Durgavati%20Medical%20College%20in%20the%20district%20by%20jail%20authorities%20in%20an%20unconscious%20state%20around%208.25%20pm%20on%20Thursday%20after%20complaining%20of%20vomiting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20patient%20was%20provided%20immediate%20medical%20care%20by%20a%20team%20of%20nine%20doctors.%20But%2C%20despite%20their%20best%20efforts%2C%20the%20patient%20died%20due%20to%20a%20cardiac%20arrest%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bulletin%2C%20which%20was%20in%20Hindi%2C%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20team%20of%20police%20personnel%20had%20been%20deployed%20outside%20the%20hospital%20shortly%20after%20Ansari%20was%20taken%20there%20and%20prohibitory%20orders%20under%20Section%20144%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Code%20(CrPC)%20have%20been%20imposed%20across%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20following%20his%20death%2C%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20Prashant%20Kumar%20said%20additional%20police%20personnel%20as%20well%20as%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20teams%20have%20also%20been%20deployed%20in%20Banda%2C%20Mau%2C%20Ghazipur%20and%20Varanasi%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarlier%20Hospitalisation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnsari%20had%20also%20been%20hospitalised%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20Tuesday%20and%20discharged%20after%20nearly%2014%20hours.%20His%20brother%2C%20Ghazipur%20MP%20Afzal%20Ansari%2C%20had%20then%20claimed%20that%20the%20gangster-turned-politician%20was%20being%20given%20a%20%26quot%3Bpoisonous%20substance%26quot%3B%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMukhtar%20said%20that%20he%20was%20given%20a%20poisonous%20substance%20in%20his%20food%20in%20jail.%20This%20happened%20for%20the%20second%20time.%20He%20was%20given%20poison%20around%2040%20days%20ago%20as%20well.%20And%2C%20recently%2C%20on%20March%2019%20or%20March%2022%2C%20he%20was%20again%20given%20this%20(poison)%20due%20to%20which%20his%20condition%20is%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20Afzal%20Ansari%20had%20been%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20PTI.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prison%20department%20had%2C%20however%2C%20said%20Ansari's%20health%20had%20deteriorated%20and%20he%20had%20fallen%20in%20the%20washroom%20before%20being%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%20around%203.45%20am%20on%20Tuesday.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20the%20sudden%20deterioration%20in%20the%20health%20of%20prisoner%20Mukhtar%20Ansari%20and%20falling%20in%20the%20toilet%20in%20the%20night%2C%20he%20was%20immediately%20given%20treatment%20by%20the%20jail%20doctor.%20After%20informing%20the%20district%20administration%2C%20a%20team%20of%20doctors%20was%20called%20by%20which%20the%20prisoner%20was%20referred%20to%20the%20medical%20college%20in%20the%20night%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20prison%20administration%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E61%20Criminal%20Cases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnsari%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Mau%2C%20had%2061%20criminal%20cases%20against%20him%2C%20of%20which%2015%20were%20on%20murder%20charges.%20He%20had%20joined%20a%20gang%20in%20the%201980s%20and%20then%20formed%20his%20own%20in%20the%201990s.%20The%20gang%20was%20involved%20in%20extortion%20and%20kidnapping%20in%20the%20Mau%2C%20Ghazipur%2C%20Varanasi%20and%20Jaunpur%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20he%20was%20charged%20under%20the%20now-scrapped%20Prevention%20of%20Terrorism%20Act%20after%20a%20machine%20gun%20was%20found%20from%20his%20hideout%20and%20had%20been%20in%20jail%20since%20the%20year%20after%20that.%20In%20April%202023%2C%20he%20was%20sentenced%20to%2010%20years%20for%20the%20murder%20of%20BJP%20MLA%20Krisnanand%20Rai%20and%2C%20on%20March%2013%20this%20year%2C%20he%20had%20been%20given%20a%20life%20term%20in%20a%20fake%20gun%20licence%20case%20from%201990.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20five%20times%20Ansari%20was%20elected%20as%20an%20MLA%20from%20Mau%2C%20two%20were%20on%20a%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20has%20condoled%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711650900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fdbrof7fo_mukhtar-ansari-ani-650_650x4