2content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDisgraced%20cryptocurrency%20wunderkind%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20was%20sentenced%20to%2025%20years%20in%20jail%20on%20Thursday%20following%20his%20conviction%20in%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20financial%20fraud%20cases%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20prosecutors%20were%20seeking%20a%20prison%20term%20of%2040-50%20years%20after%20a%20New%20York%20jury%20found%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%2C%20known%20by%20his%20initials%20SBF%2C%20guilty%20in%20November%20following%20a%20five-week%20trial%20that%20probed%20the%20one-time%20high%20roller's%20spectacular%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20told%20the%20courtroom%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bsorry%20about%20what%20happened%20at%20every%20stage.%20And%20there%20are%20things%20I%20should've%20done%20and%20things%20I%20shouldn't%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20sentence%20was%20meted%20out%20by%20US%20District%20Judge%20Lewis%20Kaplan%20who%20used%20the%20hearing%20to%20carefully%20walk%20through%20the%20financial%20crimes%20committed%20by%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20sentencing%20now%20done%2C%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20is%20expected%20to%20appeal%20his%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20New%20York%20jury%20found%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20guilty%20in%20November%20following%20the%20lengthy%20trial%20that%20probed%20his%20stunning%20downfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried's%20seven-count%20conviction%20reflective%20of%20the%20defendant's%20%26quot%3Bunmatched%20greed%20and%20hubris%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government's%20sentencing%20request%20argued%20for%20significant%20jail%20time%20in%20light%20of%20fraud%20it%20estimates%20at%20more%20than%20%2410%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20a%20lengthy%20sentence%20is%20necessary%20to%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20the%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20argued%20US%20Attorney%20Damian%20Williams%2C%20who%20characterized%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Badept%26quot%3B%20spin%20doctor%20capable%20of%20additional%20malfeasance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20government's%20proposed%20sentence%20%26quot%3Bbarbaric%2C%26quot%3B%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried's%20attorneys%20depicted%20their%20client%20as%20a%20diligent%20young%20man%20motivated%20by%20philanthropy%20who%20got%20in%20over%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20portrayal%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20SBF's%20defense%20presented%20at%20trial%20--%20which%20was%20quickly%20rejected%20by%20jurors%20after%20just%20five%20hours%20of%20deliberation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried's%20attorney's%20had%20asked%20for%20six%20years%20in%20prison%2C%20a%20sentence%20%26quot%3Bthat%20returns%20Sam%20promptly%20to%20a%20productive%20role%20in%20society%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20attorneys%20led%20by%20Marc%20Mukasey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFTX%20Implosion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20graduate%20of%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20and%20a%20billionaire%20before%20the%20age%20of%2030%2C%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20conquered%20the%20crypto%20world%20at%20breakneck%20speed%2C%20turning%20FTX%2C%20a%20small%20start-up%20he%20cofounded%20in%202019%2C%20into%20the%20world's%20second%20largest%20exchange%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20November%202022%2C%20the%20FTX%20empire%20imploded%2C%20unable%20to%20cope%20with%20massive%20withdrawal%20requests%20from%20customers%20panicked%20to%20learn%20that%20some%20of%20the%20funds%20stored%20at%20the%20company%20had%20been%20committed%20to%20risky%20operations%20at%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried's%20personal%20hedge%20fund%2C%20Alameda%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20trial%2C%20some%20of%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried's%20closest%20associates%20said%20that%20he%20was%20key%20to%20all%20the%20decisions%20that%20saw%20%248%20billion%20vanish%20from%20FTX.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20group%20included%20Caroline%20Ellison%2C%20the%20former%20Alameda%20CEO%20and%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried's%20on-and-off-again%20girlfriend%2C%20who%20testified%20that%20Alameda%20had%20stolen%20%26quot%3Baround%20%2414%20billion%26quot%3B%20from%20FTX%20clients%20and%20that%20Bankman-Fried%20%26quot%3Bdirected%20me%20to%20commit%20those%20crimes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilings%20from%20the%20prosecution%20and%20defense%20offered%20starkly%20different%20takes%20on%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%2C%20the%20son%20of%20two%20well%20regarded%20law%20professors%20at%20tony%20Stanford%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lack%20of%20contrition%20is%20galling%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Williams%2C%20who%20took%20issue%20with%20the%20image%20of%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20as%20%26quot%3Bselfless%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Baltruistic%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20championed%20by%20the%20defense%2C%20noting%20he%20used%20funds%20for%20%26quot%3Bluxury%26quot%3B%20real%20estate%2C%20donations%20to%20rub%20shoulders%20with%20political%20leaders%2C%20a%20Super%20Bowl%20television%20ad%20and%20%26quot%3Baccess%20to%20celebrities.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defense's%20statement%20describes%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20as%20%26quot%3Bwracked%26quot%3B%20with%20remorse%20over%20the%20implosion%20of%20FTX.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecovered%20funds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESam%20Bankman-Fried's%20attorneys%20also%20pointed%20to%20statements%20from%20FTX's%20current%20leaders%20expressing%20confidence%20that%20FTX%20customers%20and%20creditors%20would%20get%20back%20their%20money%2C%20saying%20in%20the%20brief%2C%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20harm%20to%20customers%2C%20lenders%20and%20investors%20is%20zero.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20argument%20drew%20a%20scathing%20response%20from%20FTX%20Trading%20Chief%20Executive%20John%20Ray%2C%20who%20said%20ongoing%20recoveries%20of%20ill-gotten%20gains%20do%20not%20make%20up%20for%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20things%20he%20stole...%20were%20successfully%20recovered%20through%20the%20efforts%20of%20a%20dedicated%20group%26quot%3B%20of%20professionals%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20mean%20the%20things%20were%20not%20stolen%2C%26quot%3B%20Ray%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20it%20means%20is%20that%20we%20got%20some%20of%20them%20back.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711643220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F95eeh5i_-sam-bankmanfried_625x300_28_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsam-bankman-fried-jailed-for-25-years-for-ftx-fraud-5329347%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Disgraced%20cryptocurrency%20wunderkind%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20was%20sentenced%20to%2025%20years%20in%20jail%20on%20Thursday%20following%20his%20conviction%20in%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20financial%20fraud%20cases%20in%20history.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fsam-bankman-fried-jailed-for-25-years-for-ftx-fraud-5329347%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNeed%20India%20To%20Restore%20Just%20And%20Lasting%20Peace%20In%20Ukraine%26quot%3B%3A%20Foreign%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20war%20with%20Russia%20rages%20on%2C%20Ukraine's%20Foreign%20Minister%2C%20Dmytro%20Kuleba%2C%20has%20said%20India%20has%20an%20important%20global%20voice%20and%20can%20not%20only%20use%20it%20to%20influence%20the%20way%20Moscow%20behaves%20but%20also%20help%20other%20nations%20join%20an%20initiative%20for%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20expansive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20on%20Thursday%20during%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Ukrainian%20leader%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20need%20for%20India%20to%20get%20a%20seat%20on%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%2C%20the%20evolving%20India-Russia%20and%20India-Ukraine%20relationship%2C%20a%20planned%20peace%20summit%20in%20Switzerland%2C%20and%20Holi%20being%20celebrated%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Kharkiv.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kuleba%2C%20who%20is%20in%20India%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%20at%20the%20invitation%20of%20Foreign%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%2C%20said%20it%20didn't%20take%20him%20any%20time%20to%20agree%20to%20come.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20because%20India%20is%20a%20very%20important%20player%20in%20the%20world%20and%20we%20need%20India%20to%20restore%20just%20and%20lasting%20peace%20in%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Mr%20Jaishankar's%20statements%20that%20India%20and%20Russia%20take%20special%20care%20of%20each%20other's%20interests%2C%20but%20also%20that%20the%20country%20has%20given%20frank%20messages%20to%20Moscow%2C%20the%20Ukrainian%20foreign%20minister%20said%20the%20India-Russia%20is%20based%20on%20the%20Soviet%20legacy%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bextinct%20and%20has%20no%20future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMentioning%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20statement%20-%20which%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bfamous%20words%26quot%3B%20-%20that%20'this%20is%20not%20an%20era%20of%20war'%2C%20Mr%20Kuleba%20said%20Russia%20has%20triggered%20the%20largest%20conflict%20in%20Europe%20since%20the%20Second%20World%20War.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20there%20are%20some%20economic%2C%20technological%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20Russia%20and%20India%20is%20a%20sovereign%20nation%2C%20it%20has%20the%20right%20to%20develop%20relations%20with%20any%20country%20it%20deems%20appropriate.%20But%20if%20India%20and%20Russia%20are%20so%20close%2C%20it%20means%20that%20India%20can%20influence%20the%20way%20Russia%20behaves%20and%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20the%20voice%20of%20India%20is%20so%20important%20but%2C%20second%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20this%20relationship%20has%20a%20future%20for%20the%20reason%20that%20I%20mentioned.%20I%20think%20the%20Ukrainian-Indian%20relationship%20has%20more%20(of%20a)%20future%20in%20that%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Key%20Role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20what%20his%20country%20would%20like%20India%20to%20do%20in%20the%20current%20situation%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20New%20Delhi%20can%20use%20its%20relations%20with%20Russia%20to%20stop%20the%20war%2C%20which%20has%20gone%20on%20for%20over%20two%20years%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20can%20play%20a%20very%20important%20role%20in%20bringing%20together%20more%20nations%20from%20the%20Global%20South...%20if%20India%20sits%20at%20the%20table%20of%20the%20peace%20formula%2C%20the%20initiative%20put%20forward%20by%20Ukraine%20to%20find%20a%20diplomatic%20solution%20to%20the%20war%2C%20then%20many%20other%20nations%20will%20feel%20much%20safer%20and%20comfortable%20sitting%20next%20to%20India%20and%20they%20will%20come%20and%20join%20this%20effort%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kuleba%20said%20this%20will%20not%20only%20enhance%20%26quot%3Bexcellent%26quot%3B%20India-Ukraine%20ties%2C%20but%20also%20respect%20for%20international%20law.%20%26quot%3BThat%20you%20cannot%20change%20borders%20by%20force%2C%20that%20you%20cannot%20invade%20your%20neighbours%2C%20that%20you%20cannot%20commit%20atrocities.%20This%20is%20the%20world%20that%20India%20will%20benefit%20from%20and%20this%20is%20the%20world%20that%20Russia%20tries%20to%20destroy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20Indicated%20a%20softening%20of%20Ukraine's%20stance%20on%20India%20purchasing%20Russian%20oil%20and%20said%20since%20the%20transaction%20is%20done%20in%20rupees%2C%20it%20does%20not%20end%20up%20benefiting%20the%20Russian%20%26quot%3Bwar%20machine%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERussian%20Attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20last%20week's%20attack%20on%20a%20Moscow%20concert%20hall%2C%20in%20which%20at%20least%20140%20people%20were%20killed%2C%20and%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20claims%20that%20the%20attackers%20were%20heading%20towards%20South%20Ukraine%2C%20Mr%20Kuleba%20said%20the%20attempt%20at%20blaming%20his%20country%20was%20no%20surprise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20rocket%20scientist.%20If%20there%20is%20anything%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20discredit%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20international%20community%2C%20if%20there%20is%20anything%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20mobilise%20more%20Russians%20against%20Ukrainians%2C%20it%20will%20be%20done.%20This%20is%20the%20attitude%20and%20the%20approach%20that%20the%20Russian%20leadership%20has%20take..%20They%20kept%20lying%20to%20the%20whole%20world%20that%20they%20were%20not%20going%20to%20invade%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20they%20did.%20They%20lie%20all%20the%20time.%20So%20why%20do%20you%20think%20they%20are%20telling%20the%20truth%20this%20time%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20On%20Security%20Council%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20minister%20said%20that%20despite%20the%20Israel-Gaza%20war%20and%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20going%20on%20simultaneously%2C%20his%20country%20has%20got%20help%20from%20Europe%20and%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BF-16s%20will%20arrive%20in%20Ukraine%20soon...%20Yes%2C%20there%20is%20a%20debate%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20we%20all%20follow%20it%20with%20popcorn%20in%20our%20hands.%20It's%20pretty%20dramatic%2C%20I%20agree%2C%20but%20both%20Democrats%20and%20Republicans%20agree%20that%20support%20to%20Ukraine%20must%20continue...%20Even%20if%20anyone%20wants%20the%20US%20to%20completely%20isolate%20itself%20and%20focus%20entirely%20on%20domestic%20issues%2C%20this%20is%20simply%20impossible.%20This%20is%20not%20how%20the%20world%20works.%20So%20the%20United%20States%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20fixing%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20the%20United%20Nations%20is%20losing%20its%20relevance%20given%20the%20continuation%20of%20the%20two%20wars%2C%20he%20said%20criticising%20the%20UN%20would%20be%20an%20easy%20thing.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20resort%20to%20this%20easy%20exercise%20because%20the%20war%20taught%20us%20that%20only%20difficult%20exercises%20are%20worth%20spending%20your%20energy%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20added%2C%20however%2C%20that%20the%20UN%20is%20struggling%20because%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20inside%20the%20organisation%20is%20%26quot%3Bbroken%26quot%3B%20and%20things%20need%20to%20change.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20new%20death%20as%20a%20result%20of%20a%20war%20in%20the%20world%20is%20another%20nail%20in%20the%20coffin%20of%20the%20United%20Nations.%20The%20UN%20is%20trying%20its%20best%2C%20but%20it%20just%20can't%20because%20it%20gets%20paralysed%20if%20there%20is%20no%20agreement%20among%20key%20stakeholders...%20It%20needs%20to%20change.%20I%20firmly%20believe%20that%20Russia%20must%20be%20out%20of%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%20India%20must%20be%20in.%20Other%20countries%20should%20become%20permanent%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20Medical%20Students%20Return%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20when%20Indian%20medical%20students%20will%20be%20able%20to%20go%20back%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20Mr%20Kulabe%20used%20the%20example%20of%20being%20treated%20by%20an%20Indian%20doctor%20a%20month%20ago%20as%20an%20example%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20India-Ukraine%20ties.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20an%20Indian%2C%20a%20young%20lady%2C%20who%20studied%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20who%20stayed%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20also%20during%20the%20war.%20And%20you%20have%20to%20understand%20that%20while%20many%20Indian%20students%20come%20back%20to%20India%20after%20studying%20in%20Ukraine%20to%20help%20their%20communities%2C%20others%20stay%20and%20become%20part%20of%20our%20community%2C%20of%20our%20society.%20Kharkiv%2C%20a%20beautiful%20city%20in%20eastern%20Ukraine%2C%20was%20the%20capital%20of%20the%20Holi%20festival%20in%20Ukraine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BEvery%20year%2C%20Indian%20students%20together%20with%20Ukrainian%20students%20turned%20the%20streets%20and%20the%20squares%20of%20Kharkiv%20into%20an%20Indian%20city%20by%20celebrating%20Holi.%20Today%2C%20the%20city%20is%20being%20systematically%20destroyed%20by%20Russia%20on%20a%20daily%20basis...%20We%20want%20Holi%20to%20be%20celebrated%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Kharkiv%20again.%20We%20don't%20want%20to%20see%20Russian%20bombs%20there%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20Russian%20soldiers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20took%20measures%20to%20allow%20foreign%20students%20to%20study%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20Ukraine.%20It's%20because%20we%20consider%20them%20part%20of%20our%20society%20and%20we%20greatly%20value%20this%20part%20of%20our%20bilateral%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20emphasised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAttempts%20At%20Peace%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20threat%20of%20a%20World%20War%2C%20which%20has%20been%20flagged%20several%20times%20by%20Mr%20Putin%2C%20the%20Ukrainian%20foreign%20minister%20said%20it%20could%20be%20rhetoric.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20President%20Putin%20loves%20his%20lavish%20life%20too%20much%20to%20put%20it%20at%20the%20risk%20of%20extinction%20by%20resorting%20to%20a%20third%20world%20war.%20But%2C%20of%20course%2C%20in%20order%20to%20persuade%20countries%20not%20to%20help%20Ukraine%2C%20he%20will%20continue%20to%20heat%20up%20his%20rhetoric.%20This%20is%20just%20rhetoric%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20peace%20summit%20is%20being%20planned%20in%20Switzerland%20at%20Ukraine's%20request%20and%20Mr%20Kuleba%20said%20India's%20presence%20there%20will%20be%20critical.%20%26quot%3B(It%20will%20be)%20crucial%20and%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20I%20am%20here.%20India%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20preparatory%20coordination%20meetings%20and%20President%20Voldymyr%20Zelensky%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20discussed%20the%20summit%20in%20their%20phone%20conversation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20summit%20is%20based%20on%20a%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20resolution%20of%20October%202022%20on%20the%20main%20principles%20of%20restoring%20peace%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Mr%20Kuleba%20pointed%20out%20that%20143%20nations%20had%20voted%20in%20its%20favour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20say%20anything%20more%20than%20what%20is%20already%20said%20in%20this%20resolution.%20So%20those%20countries%20who%20voted%20for%20this%20resolution%20should%20face%20no%20problem%20in%20supporting%20what%20is%20written%20in%20the%20peace%20formula.%20And%20143%20is%20a%20big%20number%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20some%20of%20the%20main%20points%20of%20the%20formula%20are%20food%20security%2C%20energy%20security%2C%20exchange%20of%20prisoners%2C%20return%20of%20deported%20children%20and%20accountability%20for%20the%20crimes%20committed%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20the%20main%20aim%20is%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20basically%20the%20peace%20formula%20is%20a%20menu%20that%20addresses%20all%20major%20problems%20caused%20by%20the%20large-scale%20invasion%20of%20Russia%20in%20Ukraine.%20And%20we%20designed%20this%20menu%2C%20I%20deliberately%20use%20the%20word%20'menu'%2C%20in%20a%20way%20that%20any%20country%20can%20pick%20up%20the%20issue%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20work%20on.%20For%20example%2C%20you%20want%20to%20work%20on%20the%20exchange%20of%20prisoners%2C%20but%20you%20do%20not%20want%20to%20work%20on%20bringing%20Russian%20leadership%20to%20account%20for%20war%20crimes%20committed%20in%20Ukraine.%20And%20that's%20fine...%20It%20allows%20us%20to%20have%20more%20countries%20on%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELessons%20From%20The%20Mahatma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAsked%20about%20a%20video%20he%20had%20posted%20with%20a%20statue%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20behind%20him%20-%20in%20which%20he%20spoke%20of%20the%20freedom%20fighter's%20legacy-%20and%20what%20he%20expects%20to%20achieve%20in%20the%20conversations%20with%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20and%20others%20in%20the%20government%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20he%20expects%20a%20candid%20exchange.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kulabe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20have%20a%20very%20candid%20conversation%2C%20about%20all%20the%20good%20things%2C%20and%20the%20things%20that%20we%20dislike%20in%20our%20policies%20-%20I%20mean%20in%20Ukrainian%20policy%2C%20but%20also%20in%20Indian%20policy.%20But%2C%20since%20I%20will%20be%20seeing%20Dr%20Jaishankar%20tomorrow%2C%20I%20can%20give%20him%20a%20heads%20up%20to%20our%20conversation%20thanks%20to%20your%20question.%20My%20point%20is%20very%20simple.%20Very%20few%20believed%20that%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20would%20succeed%2C%20and%20India%20would%20become%20an%20independent%20nation%20through%20a%20peaceful%20resistance.%20And%20today%2C%20many%20say%20that%20Ukraine%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20restore%20its%20territorial%20integrity%2C%20but%20the%20Mahatma%20succeeded%2C%20and%20Ukraine%20will%20succeed%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20truth%20was%20on%20his%20side%2C%20and%20is%20on%20our%20side%20today.%20And%20I'm%20sure%20that%20India%20will%20be%20on%20the%20side%20of%20truth%20again%20because%20supporting%20Ukraine%20today%20is%20supporting%20the%20legacy%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20-%20freedom%2C%20independence%2C%20and%20belief%20that%20if%20you%20fight%20for%20the%20right%20cause%2C%20you%20will%20eventually%20succeed%2C%20irrespective%20of%20how%20strong%20your%20enemy%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711641600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fbftccr1_dmytro-kuleba_625x300_28_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneed-india-to-restore-just-and-lasting-peace-in-ukraine-foreign-minister-5329151%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20war%20with%20Russia%20rages%20on%2C%20Ukraine's%20Foreign%20Minister%2C%20Dmytro%20Kuleba%2C%20has%20said%20India%20has%20an%20important%20global%20voice%20and%20can%20not%20only%20use%20it%20to%20influence%20the%20way%20Moscow%20behaves%20but%20also%20help%20other%20nations%20join%20an%20initiative%20for%20peace.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneed-india-to-restore-just-and-lasting-peace-in-ukraine-foreign-minister-5329151%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Hardik%20To%20Tell...%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex%20India%20Star%20On%20Why%20His%20Absence%20Good%20For%20GT%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGujarat%20Titans'%20new%20era%20under%20the%20captaincy%20of%20young%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20bittersweet%20beginning%20in%20IPL%202024.%20The%202022%20champions%20began%20this%20season%20by%20defeating%20their%20old%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Mumbai%20Indians%20by%20six%20runs.%20However%2C%20their%20IPL%202023%20final%20rivals%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20edged%