not%20do%20his%20side%20any%20favours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20strike%20rate%20of%20MI%20batters...%20Hardik%20Pandya%20is%20a%20big-hitting%20player%2C%20but%20he%20struck%20at%20only%20120.%20Yes%2C%20the%20bowling%20was%20good%20at%20that%20time%2C%20but%20one%20thing%20that%20irked%20me%20was%20the%20shots%20he%20hit%20against%20back-of-length.%20He%20was%20hitting%20the%20shots%20down%20the%20ground%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tiwary%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dp7Jyh-pqCg0%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGenerally%2C%20when%20the%20asking%20rate%20is%2014-15%2C%20and%20you%20have%20such%20a%20big%20player%2C%20you'd%20want%20them%20to%20at%20least%20try%20for%20a%20six.%20Attempting%20to%20get%20a%20single%20or%20two%2C%20or%20even%20a%20four%2C%20wasn't%20the%20demand%20of%20the%20situation.%20That%20irked%20me.%20And%20that%20shows%20he%20is%20not%20in%20good%20form.%20In%20the%20last%20match%2C%20he%20did%20start%20well%20but%20was%20dismissed.%20We%20have%20seen%20that%20he%20has%20rescued%20the%20team%20on%20many%20occasions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%C2%A0while%20speaking%20at%20the%20post-match%20presentation%2C%C2%A0Pandya%C2%A0said%20that%20the%20wicket%20was%20'good'%20at%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20International%20Stadium%20in%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20accepted%20that%20they%20have%20a%20'young%20bowling%20attack'%20and%20they%20will%20learn%20from%20the%2031-run%20loss%20against%20the%20Hyderabad-based%20franchise.%20The%20MI%20skipper%20showered%20praise%20on%20the%20Proteas%20pacer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kwena%20Maphaka%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F114998-kwena-maphaka-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKwena%20Maphaka%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20that%20he%20was%20'fantastic'%20in%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20really%20(thought%20SRH%20would%20score%20277%20at%20the%20tos