0from%20Chhindwara%20by%20his%20party%2C%20has%20declared%20assets%20worth%20nearly%20Rs%20700%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20his%20election%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENakul%20Nath%20is%20among%20the%20113%20candidates%20who%20have%20filed%20their%20nomination%20papers%20for%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20the%20central%20state%20on%20April%2019.%20The%20filing%20of%20nomination%20papers%20for%20this%20phase%20drew%20to%20a%20close%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20his%20affidavit%2C%20Nakul%20Nath's%20wealth%20has%20gone%20up%20by%20Rs%2040%20crore%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20latest%20submission%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20Nakul%20Nath%20has%20declared%20movable%20property%2C%20including%20cash%2C%20shares%20and%20bonds%2C%20worth%20Rs%20649.51%20crore%20and%20Rs%2048.07%20crore%20of%20immovable%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sitting%20Chhindwara%20MP%2C%20son%20of%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20influential%20Congress%20leader%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20had%20topped%20the%20list%20of%20475%20Lok%20Sabha%20crorepati%20members%20in%202019%2C%20according%20to%20the%20non-profit%20Association%20of%20Democratic%20Reforms%20(ADR).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20ADR%2C%20the%20entrepreneur%20politician%20had%20declared%20assets%20worth%20Rs%20660%20crore%20in%202019%20when%20he%20contested%20from%20Chhindwara%2C%20the%20pocket%20borough%20of%20his%20father%2C%20and%20emerged%20as%20the%20only%20Congress%20winner%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20year%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%2028%20of%20the%2029%20seats%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamal%20Nath%2C%20who%20successfully%20contested%20from%20Chhindwara%2C%20had%20declared%20assets%20worth%20Rs%20134%20crore%20in%20his%20poll%20affidavit%20ahead%20of%20last%20year's%20assembly%20elections%2C%20according%20to%20ADR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Nakul%20Nath%20frequently%20uses%20an%20aircra