0%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fon3gqeq8_kamal-nath-with-son-nakul-nath-ani_625x300_28_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-elections-congress-veteran-kamal-naths-son-nakul-nath-declares-assets-worth-rs-700-crore-5327873%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nakul%20Nath%2C%20the%20lone%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20who%20has%20been%20renominated%20from%20Chhindwara%20by%20his%20party%2C%20has%20declared%20assets%20worth%20nearly%20Rs%20700%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20his%20election%20affidavit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-lok-sabha-elections-congress-veteran-kamal-naths-son-nakul-nath-declares-assets-worth-rs-700-crore-5327873%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%2C%20Ambani%20Collaborate%20-%20Reliance%20Picks%20Stake%20In%20Adani%20Project.%20A%20First%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20collaboration%20between%20billionaires%2C%20Mukesh%20Ambani's%20Reliance%20Industries%20has%20picked%20up%20a%2026%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20a%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20power%20project%20of%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20and%20signed%20a%20pact%20to%20use%20the%20plants'%20500%20MW%20of%20electricity%20for%20captive%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReliance%20will%20pick%20up%205%20crore%20equity%20shares%20in%20Mahan%20Energen%20Ltd%2C%20a%20wholly%20owned%20subsidiary%20of%20Adani%20Power%20Ltd%2C%20of%20face%20value%20Rs%2010%20at%20par%20(Rs%2050%20crore)%20and%20will%20use%20500%20MW%20of%20generation%20capacity%20for%20captive%20use%2C%20the%20two%20firms%20said%20in%20separate%20stock%20exchange%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20businessmen%20hailing%20from%20Gujarat%20have%20often%20been%20pitted%20by%20media%20and%20commentators%20against%20each%20other%20but%20they%20have%20for%20years%20tiptoed%20around%20each%20other%20to%20reach%20the%20top%20two%20rungs%20of%20Asia's%20wealth%20ladder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Mr%20Ambani's%20interests%20spanning%20oil%20and%20gas%20to%20retail%20and%20telecom%20and%20Mr%20Adani's%20focus%20on%20infrastructure%20spanning%20sea%20ports%20to%20airports%2C%20coal%20and%20mining%2C%20they%20rarely%20crossed%20each%20other's%20path%20except%20in%20the%20clean%20energy%20business%20where%20the%20two%20have%20announced%20multi-billion%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adani%20aspires%20to%20be%20the%20world's%20largest%20renewable%20energy%20producer%20by%202030%20while%20Reliance%20is%20building%20four%20gigafactories%20at%20Jamnagar%20in%20Gujarat%20--%20one%20each%20for%20solar%20panels%2C%20batteries%2C%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20and%20fuel%20cells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adani%20is%20also%20building%20three%20giga%20factories%20for%20manufacturing%20solar%20modules%2C%20wind%20turbines%20and%20hydrogen%20electrolysers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20clash%20was%20also%20forecast%20when%20Adani%20group%20applied%20to%20participate%20in%20an%20auction%20of%20spectrum%20or%20airwaves%20capable%20of%20carrying%20fifth%20generation%20(5G)%20data%20and%20voice%20services.%20However%2C%20unlike%20Mr%20Ambani%2C%20Mr%20Adani%20bought%20400%20MHz%20spectrum%20in%20the%2026%20GHz%20band%2C%20which%20is%20not%20for%20public%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20the%20two%20have%20been%20far%20from%20rivals.%20In%202022%2C%20a%20firm%20with%20erstwhile%20links%20to%20Mr%20Ambani%20sold%20its%20stake%20in%20news%20broadcaster%20NDTV%20to%20Adani%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20the%20takeover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdani%20was%20also%20present%20at%20pre-wedding%20celebrations%20of%20Ambani's%20youngest%20son%2C%20Anant%2C%20at%20Jamnagar%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMahan%20Energen%20Ltd%20(MEL)%2C%20wholly%20owned%20subsidiary%20of%20Adani%20Power%20Ltd%20(APL)%2C%20has%20entered%20into%20a%2020-year%20long-term%20power%20purchase%20agreement%20(PPA)%20for%20500%20MW%20with%20Reliance%20Industries%20Ltd%20(RIL)%2C%20under%20the%20captive%20user%20policy%20as%20defined%20under%20the%20Electricity%20Rules%2C%202005%2C%26quot%3B%20Adani%20Power%20said%20in%20the%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20unit%20of%20600%20MW%20capacity%20of%20MEL's%20Mahan%20thermal%20power%20plant%2C%20out%20of%20its%20aggregate%20operating%20and%20upcoming%20capacity%20of%202%2C800%20MW%2C%20will%20be%20designated%20as%20the%20captive%20unit%20for%20this%20purpose.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20generating%20plant%20declared%20as%20a%20captive%20generating%20plant%20(CGP)%20is%20required%20to%20abide%20by%20the%20rules%20that%20state%20that%20the%20captive%20user(s)%20consuming%20the%20power%20generated%20from%20the%20captive%20generating%20plant%20for%20self-use%20must%20necessarily%20hold%20not%20less%20than%2026%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20ownership%20in%20the%20captive%20generating%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20order%20to%20avail%20the%20benefit%20of%20this%20policy%2C%20RIL%20has%20to%20hold%20a%2026%20per%20cent%20ownership%20stake%20in%20the%20captive%20unit%20in%20proportion%20to%20the%20total%20capacity%20of%20the%20power%20plant.%20It%20will%20accordingly%20invest%20in%205%20crore%20equity%20shares%20of%20MEL%2C%20aggregating%20to%20Rs%2050%20crore%20for%20the%20proportionate%20ownership%20stake%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20development%20brings%20between%20two%20corporates%20an%20exclusive%20arrangement%20for%20500%20MW%20of%20power%20purchase%20by%20Reliance%20Industries%20on%20a%20long-term%20basis.%26quot%3B%20It%20is%20unclear%20where%20Reliance%20intends%20to%20use%20the%20MEL%20power.%20It%20already%20has%20captive%20units%20at%20mega%20oil%20refining%20and%20petrochemical%20complexes%20in%20Gujarat%20and%20Maharashtra%20and%20its%20coal-bed%20methane%20(CBM)%20extractions%20in%20Sohagpur%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20may%20not%20need%20500%20MW%20of%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20connection%2C%20APL%2C%20MEL%2C%20and%20RIL%20have%20signed%20an%20investment%20agreement%20on%2027th%20March%202024%20at%207%3A00%20pm.%20Closing%20of%20the%20transaction%20is%20subject%20to%20customary%20closing%20conditions%20including%20receipt%20of%20requisite%20approvals%2C%26quot%3B%20Adani%20Power%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReliance%20in%20the%20filing%20made%20a%20similar%20disclosure%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BMEL%2C%20a%20company%20engaged%20in%20generation%20and%20supply%20of%20power%2C%20was%20incorporated%20on%20October%2019%2C%202005.%20The%20turnover%20of%20MEL%2C%20as%20per%20its%20audited%20standalone%20financial%20statement%2C%20for%20financial%20years%202022-23%2C%202021-22%20and%202020-21%20was%20Rs%202%2C730.68%20crore%2C%20Rs%201%2C393.59%20crore%20and%20Rs%20692.03%20crore%2C%20respectively.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20investment%20is%20subject%20to%20customary%20conditions%20precedent%20including%20receipt%20of%20requisite%20approvals%20by%20MEL%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20within%202%20weeks%20of%20receipt%20of%20completion%20of%20conditions%20precedent%20and%20receipt%20of%20such%20approvals%20by%20MEL%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711633440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fi2od59d_adani-ambani-gautam-adani-mukesh-ambani-ani_625x300_28_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-ambani-collaborate-reliance-picks-stake-in-adani-power-project-a-first-532800