ongress%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20joined%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20at%20the%20time%20of%20election%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovinda%2C%20who%20gave%20multiple%20superhit%20films%20in%20his%20decades-long%20career%2C%20made%20a%20blockbuster%20entry%20in%20electoral%20politics%20in%202004.%20That%20year%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BHero%20No.%201%26quot%3B%20actor%20emerged%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgiant%20killer%26quot%3B%20when%2C%20as%20the%20Congress%20candidate%2C%20he%20defeated%20BJP%20stalwart%20Ram%20Naik%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20North%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEknath%20Shinde%20welcomed%20the%2060-year-old%20actor%20into%20his%20party%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20a%20popular%20figure%20in%20all%20sections%20of%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20occasion%2C%20an%20emotional%20Govinda%2C%20who%20started%20his%20acting%20career%20in%20the%201980s%20and%20whose%20films%20were%20family%20entertainers%2C%20said%20after%20his%20first%20stint%20in%20politics%20from%202004%20to%202009%2C%20he%20never%20felt%20he%20would%20again%20come%20back%20to%20the%20same%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20back%20(in%20politics)%20after%20a%2014-year-long%20'vanvas'%20(exile)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20veteran%20actor%2C%20whose%20full%20name%20is%20Govinda%20Ahuja%2C%20said%20he%20would%20work%20in%20the%20art%20and%20culture%20field%20if%20given%20a%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20looks%20more%20beautiful%20and%20developed%20since%20Shinde%20has%20become%20CM%2C%20he%20remarked%20after%20his%20re-entry%20into%20politics%2C%20albeit%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20a%20different%20political%20party%2C%20which%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20country%20is%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20said%20development%20of%20the%20country%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20unbelievable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEknath%20Shinde%2C%20who%20took%20over%20as%20CM%20in%20June%202022%2C%20said%20there%20is%20positivity%20and%20prosperity%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20pollution%20levels%20are%20also%20coming%20down%20in%20the%20metropolis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20maintained%20the%20versatile%20actor%20has%20joined%20his%20party%20without%20any%20pre-conditions%20and%20rejected%20suggestions%20that%20the%20entry%20was%20linked%20to%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGovinda%20stands%20for%20progress.%20He%20is%20impressed%20with%20Modiji's%20development%20policies.%20He%20wants%20to%20do%20something%20for%20the%20welfare%20and%20progress%20of%20the%20film%20industry.%20I%20am%20sure%20he%20will%20be%20the%20link%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20film%20industry.%20He%20has%20joined%20us%20without%20any%20conditions%2C%26quot%3B%20Eknath%20Shinde%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGovinda%20has%20ended%20his%20vanvas%20and%20come%20to%20Ram%20rajya%2C%26quot%3B%20noted%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%2C%20whose%20party%20is%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20government%20is%20pro-development%20and%20pro-people%2C%20and%20he%20was%20impressed%20(with%20its%20policies)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20the%20actor%20will%20be%20fielded%20from%20the%20Mumbai%20North-West%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde%20clarified%20he%20hadn't%20put%20any%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20just%20wants%20to%20work%20for%20the%20film%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20Govinda%20hasn't%20joined%20the%20party%20for%20an%20election%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEknath%20Shinde%20said%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20which%20heads%20the%20governing%20'Mahayuti'%20coalition%20in%20the%20state%2C%20will%20soon%20release%20its%20list%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Mahayuti%20is%20contesting%20all%2048%20seats%20(in%20Maharashtra).%20Ours%20is%20not%20a%20government%20which%20runs%20from%20home.%20We%20are%20field%20people%20and%20work%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CM%20maintained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20coalition%20consists%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20NCP%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20leader%20Jayant%20Patil%20calling%20Govinda%20a%20%26quot%3Bflop%20actor%26quot%3B%2C%20Shinde%20emphasised%20that%20insulting%20a%20film%20artist%20amounts%20to%20showing%20disrespect%20to%20the%20entire%20entertainment%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Vijay%20Shivtare%20contesting%20from%20the%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20the%20home%20turf%20of%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20in%20Pune%20district%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde%20said%20his%20colleague%20has%20clarified%20that%20the%20party's%20decision%20on%20the%20matter%20was%20final%20for%20him%20and%20added%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20thankful%20to%20him%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711631460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fudmtr52o_actor-govinda-joins-shiv-sena-ani_625x300_28_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgovinda-returns-to-politics-after-14-year-vanvaas-joins-shiv-sena-praises-eknath-shinde-5327821%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bollywood%20actor%20and%20former%20Congress%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Govinda%20today%20joined%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20in%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-new