s'%20head%20coach%20Chandrakant%20Pandit%2C%20whose%20coaching%20style%20was%20termed%20%E2%80%9Cmilitant%E2%80%9D%20by%20former%20KKR%20all-rounder%20David%20Wiese.%20Wiese%2C%20who%20now%20plies%20his%20trade%20for%20Namibia%2C%20claimed%20that%20many%20foreign%20players%20in%20the%20roster%20of%20KKR%20were%20frustrated%20by%20Pandit's%20tough%20style%20of%20functioning%20during%20last%20year's%20IPL.%20However%2C%20Jamaican%20Russell%2C%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20KKR's%20core%20group%2C%20sounded%20different.%20%E2%80%9CWe've%20been%20working%20with%20him%20from%20last%20year.%20I%20think%20when%20you're%20working%20with%20a%20coach%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20you%20have%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20adjust%20to%20their%20philosophy.%20There%20have%20to%20be%20rules.%20We%20are%20professionals.%20So%2C%20we%20don't%20complain%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Russell%20during%20the%20pre-match%20press%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20try%20to%20do%20the%20best%20for%20this%20franchise.%20He's%20been%20doing%20an%20amazing%20job%2C%20and%20we've%20gotten%20coming%20back%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandit%2C%20who%20is%20known%20as%20a%20disciplinarian%2C%20had%20taken%20over%20as%20KKR%20coach%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202022%20after%20Brendon%20McCullum%20accepted%20England's%20head%20coach%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20(Pandit)%20is%20known%20in%20India%20as%20a%20very%20militant%20type%20of%20coach.%20He%20is%20very%20strict%2C%20very%20disciplinarian%20that%20type%20of%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20in%20franchise%20cricket%2C%20when%20you%20have%20overseas%20guys%2C%20who've%20played%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20they%20don't%20need%20anyone%20coming%20and%20telling%20them%20how%20they%20need%20to%20behave%2C%20what%20they%20need%20to%20wear%20and%20what%20they%20need%20to%20do%20the%20whole%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20that%20was%20tough%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Wiese%20on%20the%20podcast%20%E2%80%98Hitman%20for%20Hire%3A%20A%20year%20in%20the%20life%20of%20a%20franchise%20cricketer'%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711629120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fpm6lr5do_as_625x300_28_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fandre-russell-breaks-silence-after-ex-kkr-star-calls-head-coach-militant-5327775%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andre%20Russell%20supported%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders'%20head%20coach%20Chandrakant%20Pandit%2C%20whose%20coaching%20style%20was%20termed%20%26quot%3Bmilitant%26quot%3B%20by%20former%20KKR%20all-rounder%20David%20Wiese.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFew%20Can%20Score%20As%20Much%20As%20Me%2C%20But...%26quot%3B%3A%20Sachin%20Pilot%20On%20Not%20Contesting%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Sachin%20Pilot%20has%20said%20the%20decision%20not%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20is%20a%20calculated%20one%20and%2C%20using%20a%20cricket%20analogy%2C%20claimed%20few%20people%20can%20score%20as%20many%20runs%20for%20his%20party%20as%20him%20when%20he%20enters%20the%20electoral%20playground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20a%20question%20at%20the%20NDTV%20Yuva%20conclave%20on%20Thursday%20on%20why%20he%20was%20not%20stepping%20into%20the%20electoral%20playground%20when%20young%20leaders%20like%20him%20could%20effect%20change%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%20the%20party%20has%20taken%20a%20call%20after%20taking%20several%20factors%20into%20account%20and%20his%20responsibility%2C%20as%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20in-charge%2C%20is%20also%20an%20important%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20step%20into%20the%20ground%20and%20bat%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20other%20people%20can%20score%20as%20many%20runs%20as%20I%20do%20for%20the%20Congress.%20But%20people%20have%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20what%20responsibility%20they%20are%20given%20when%20they%20enter%20the%20ground.%20As%20a%20Congress%20general%20secretary%2C%20I%20have%20been%20given%20charge%20of%20Chhattisgarh.%20Who%20contests%20an%20election%2C%20who%20is%20involved%20in%20strategy%2C%20who%20works%20for%20the%20organisation%2C%20all%20of%20these%20are%20decided%20differently%20at%20different%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%20in%20Hindi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202004%2C%20I%20was%20an%20MP.%20Then%20I%20was%20an%20MLA.%20I%20was%20also%20a%20Union%20minister%20and%20a%20state%20Congress%20chief.%20So%2C%20I%20am%20carrying%20out%20the%20responsibilities%20that%20have%20been%20entrusted%20to%20me.%20The%20candidates%20that%20have%20been%20picked%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20have%20been%20decided%20after%20a%20lot%20of%20thought%20and%20they%20are%20people%20that%20can%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20leader%20said%20even%20people%20who%20are%20not%20fighting%20the%20polls%20have%20important%20roles%20to%20play%20and%20have%20to%20deliver%2C%20just%20like%20he%20has%20to%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20the%20Congress%20will%20win%20the%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%20some%20parties%20are%20talking%20about%20things%20like%20getting%20more%20than%20400%20seats%20and%20that%20politics%20today%20is%20reeking%20of%20arrogance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20advertisements%20and%20what%20is%20actually%20happening%20on%20the%20ground.%20The%20gulf%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20poor%20and%20between%20cities%20and%20villages%20is%20widening.%20Economic%20policies%20are%20responsible%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20suspense%20over%20the%20Congress%20strongholds%20of%20Amethi%20and%20Rae%20Bareli%20and%20whether%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20will%20be%20contesting%20from%20there%2C%20the%20leader%20did%20not%20give%20a%20clear%20answer%20and%20said%20Mr%20Gandhi%20has%20been%20named%20as%20a%20candidate%20from%20the%20Wayanad%20seat%20in%20Kerala.%20He%20said%20the%20two%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20seats%20have%20been%20Congress%20bastions%20and%20the%20party%20will%20win%20there%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'2004%20Repeat'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pilot%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20NDA%20of%20former%20prime%20minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee's%20time%20had%20been%20finished%20and%20the%20BJP%20began%20reviving%20it%20after%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20parties%20formed%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202019%2C%2065%25%20of%20the%20votes%20went%20to%20parties%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%20So%2C%20only%2035%25%20of%20people%20supported%20the%20BJP...%20If%20the%20BJP%20is%20so%20confident%2C%20why%20is%20it%20inducting%20people%20from%20the%20opposition%3F%20This%20will%20be%20an%20interesting%20election%20and%20there%20will%20be%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%202004%20polls%20when%20the%20opposition%20won%20despite%20people%20expecting%20an%20NDA%20victory%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711628880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fe6utekl8_sachin-pilot_625x300_28_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-yuva-conclave-few-can-score-as-much-as-me-but-sachin-pilot-on-not-fighting-lok-sabha-polls-5327772%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Sachin%20Pilot%20has%20said%20the%20decision%20not%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20is%20a%20calculated%20one%20and%2C%20using%20a%20cricket%20analogy%2C%20claimed%20few%20people%20can%20score%20as%20many%20runs%20for%20his%20party%20as%20him%20when%20he%20enters%20the%20electoral%20playground.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-yuva-conc