%3EOne%20of%20the%20customers%2C%20Gavin%2C%20who%20stayed%20at%20the%20property%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20really%20feels%20like%20home.%20Living%20at%20their%20place%20with%20all%20the%20exquisite%20architecture%20depicting%20our%20Tamil%20culture%20was%20an%20experience%20of%20a%20lifetime.%20It%20is%20huge%20in%20size%20with%20several%20areas%20to%20relax%20but%20the%20uniqueness%20was%20in%20the%20small%20details%20like%20the%20way%20they%20treated%20us.%20The%20food%2C%20their%20accommodating%20behaviour%20made%20our%20stay%20very%20enjoyable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussing%20future%20plans%2C%20Rajchandar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20really%20want%20to%20expand%20the%20property%20as%20many%20people%20want%20to%20stay%2C%20but%20we%20are%20often%20fully%20booked.%20We%20also%20aim%20to%20incorporate%20more%20sustainable%20measures%20like%20solar%20energy%20into%20the%20current%20homestay.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20book%20your%20stay%20at%20this%20Rajchandar%E2%80%99s%20homestay%20by%20reaching%20them%20at%209360946642%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20Pictures%20Credit%3A%20Rajchandar)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711524048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fbook-hotel-12-1711118400.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345629%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Looking%20for%20the%20best%20homestays%20in%20Kanyakumari%3F%20Rajchandar%20Padmanaban%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Naga%20Jeyalakshmi%2C%20built%20Muthunandhini%20Palace%20as%20a%20heritage%20home%20where%20sustainability%20meets%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20traditional%20architecture.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345629%2Fmuthunandhini-palace-kanyakumari-ecofriendly-homestay-chettinad-architecture-tamil-nadu-travel-destination%2F%