0on%20behalf%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Earth%20Sciences%20(MoES)%20revealed%20a%20rise%20of%200.7%20degrees%20Celsius%20surface%20air%20temperature%20from%201901%20to%202018%20and%20a%20rise%20of%201%20degree%20Celsius%20sea%20surface%20temperatures%20in%20the%20tropical%20Indian%20Ocean%20from%201951%20to%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20climate%20action%20startups%2C%20you%20ask%3F%20Why%20not%3F%E2%80%9D%20She%20emphasises%20how%20Tvaran%20is%20tying%20two%20goals%20into%20one%20by%20backing%20women%20business%20owners%20and%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20champions%20of%20climate%20advocacy.%20Early-stage%20women%20entrepreneurs%20are%20being%20supported%20by%20helping%20them%20amplify%20their%20market%20presence.%20This%20is%20being%20achieved%20by%20giving%20them%20access%20to%20markets%20and%20finance%2C%20which%20will%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20help%20them%20commercialise%20and%20scale%20their%20ventures%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kalyani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201805px)%20100vw%2C%201805px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221805%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20sectors%20where%20women%20are%20taking%20charge%20of%20businesses%20has%20expanded%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005.jpeg%201805w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FIMG_7814_11zon-1710833005-1152x1536.jpeg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-m